api_list.description:
Get all cities and store counts in a particular state
    Use brand filter to get cities for the brand

Example Payload
 {
    "api_key":"iopII2344_ADDDxxw1i1",
    "state":"CA",                    
    "brand_alias": "western-union" (optional)
 }
Example Response
 [{

    "city": "Los Angeles",
    "store_count": 630,
    "state","CA"
  },
  {

    "city": "Newyork",
    "store_count": 1200,
    "state":"NY"
  }]

